"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Over the past year, we have witnessed the exponential growth of Layer2 ecosystem, such as Polygon, Avalanche, Optimism, and Arbitrum. Although, there are official cross-chain bridges, however, it takes long time (7 days) to cross back to the mainnet. To solve this problem, there are few cross-chain platforms, that provide instant liquidity to users to cross among different chains. Based on my research and hands-on experience, I have found the following cross-chain platforms, that are safe, user-friendly, and fast. \\n\\n1. Hop.exchange. You can cross assets among Ethereum Mainnet, Polygon, xDai, Optimism, Arbitrum. \\n2. Across.to. This is a new project, currently, you can only cross from Arbitrum to Mainnet, and it is extremely fast, usually take 2 minutes. You can also add liquidity to the platform. \\n3.  Xpollinate.io. This is also a good cross-chain platform powered by connext. However, I find the liquidity is sometimes limited, and “couldn’t find a route”. Hopefully, as more users use this platform, there will be more liquidity to use. \\n\\n   [https://www.xpollinate.io/](https://www.xpollinate.io/)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1638085011,\"title\":\"Top Cross-chain Platforms\"},\"digest\":\"sDzL-Yan92SwYaCiU4M1JG7rmORk66xywWaqbpxd2Ik\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4f136028ec25350d74Bd963b5c22b9aB4F622BF2\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"Atgsuc31ebrQU-qL4zfCkVtDQvXb93VidU94Q3XyvuM\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xAqkJztk6Ozaxb-ULp9HdzPTOXofqXfYThxS0v96p2c\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MAgMEZRFoZCWNUjTXnHFeX0hWHEH0K0l6rqLXR25NLQotarU193HSg3AgX7o6eDGMRqNIdVhILN_5A8B8ZNqTQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd582722faced1a0150ea1c8aa5c21a9a0878c3c4418c1d958a0183af46214e2a2c4388a2949d9cfc02766478cb5d4acf9424354f28192d72fbd7c7c41f99f59d1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":tr